  <script>
   jQuery(window).load(function(){
					//jQuery('img.lazy').asynchImageLoader({callback : function(){
												jQuery('ul.get_thumb_list li a img').each(function(){
							jQuery(this).load(function(){
								jQuery(this).parent('a').css('background-image', 'none');
							});
						});
						/*taxonomy start*/
						jQuery('#filters a').click(function(){
							var selector = jQuery(this).attr('data-filter');
							jQuery('.taxonomy_filter').isotope({ filter: selector ,sortBy:'random' }).isotope('reloadItems');
							jQuery('.taxonomy_item a.popup').attr('rel', 'all_items');
							jQuery('.taxonomy_item.isotope-hidden a.popup').attr('rel', '');
							return false;
						});
						jQuery('#options').find('.info_filters a').click(function(){
							var $this = jQuery(this);
							if ( !$this.hasClass('sel_item') ) {
								$this.parents('.info_filters').find('.sel_item').removeClass('sel_item');
								$this.addClass('sel_item');
							}
						});
						jQuery(document).ready(function(e) {
							jQuery('.taxonomy_filter').isotope({
								itemSelector : '.taxonomy_item'
							});
						});
						/*taxonomy end*/
						jQuery('.bar_menu_loading img.fifty').attr('src', '/img/ajax-loader.gif').load(function(){
							jQuery('div.bar_menu_loading span').remove();
							var w=jQuery('div.bar_menu_loading').width();
							var neww=-(w/2);
							jQuery('div.bar_menu_loading').css('margin-left',-55);
						});

					//}});
				});
  </script>

           <div class="head_post">
            <h2 class="post_title">
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/now-wpthemegenerator-is-responsive-2/" rel="bookmark" title="WP theme generator themes are full responsive (mobile ready)">
              WP theme generator themes are full responsive (mobile ready)
             </a>
            </h2>
            <span class="comments_link" data-show="true">
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/now-wpthemegenerator-is-responsive-2/#respond">
              <span class="dsq-postid" rel="4096 http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/?p=4096">
               0
              </span>
             </a>
            </span>
            <span class="post_author post_icon" data-show="true">
             By admin
            </span>
            <span class="post_date post_icon" data-show="true">
             On  July 13, 2012
            </span>
            <span class="post_categ post_icon" data-show="true">
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">
              Uncategorized
             </a>
            </span>
            <span class="post_commts post_icon" data-show="true">
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/now-wpthemegenerator-is-responsive-2/#respond">
              <span class="dsq-postid" rel="4096 http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/?p=4096">

            <span class="post_tag post_icon" data-show="true">

           <!-- head_post -->
           <div class="entry_post ">
            <p>
             Now wpthemegenerator is responsive, you can now enjoy this wonderful tool from a mobile device without any problem, not matter if its a mobile, tablet, ipad etc. You can enable/disable the responsive mode from the dashboard.
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/features/">
              Please check all theme generator features.
             </a>
            </p>
            <p>
             <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4098" src="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/responsive_121.jpg" style="border: 5px solid white; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.496094) 0px 0px 4px; margin: 30px auto; width: 95%;" title="responsive_1"/>
            </p>
            <p>
            </p>
            <p>
             Responsive Web Design (RWD) essentially indicates that a web site is crafted to use Cascading Style Sheets 3 media queries, an extension of the @media rule, with fluid proportion-based grids (which use percentages and EMs instead of pixels), to adapt the layout to the viewing environment, and probably also use flexible images. As a result, users across a broad range of devices and browsers will have access to a single source of content, laid out so as to be easy to read and navigate with a minimum of resizing, panning, and scrolling.
             <a class="more-link" href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/now-wpthemegenerator-is-responsive-2/#more-4096">
              <span class="more-link_right">
              </span>
              Read More
              <span class="more-link_left">
              </span>
             </a>
            </p>
           </div>
           <!-- end entry_post -->

            </a>
            <p>
             Now wpthemegenerator is responsive, you can now enjoy this wonderful tool from a mobile device without any problem, not matter if its a mobile, tablet, ipad etc. You can enable/disable the responsive mode from the dashboard.Please check all theme generator features.  Responsive Web Design (RWD) essentially indicates that a web site is crafted to []
            </p>
           </div>

           <!-- head_post -->
           <div class="entry_post ">
            <p>
             The WP Theme Generator team adds new features every day, thus increasing the possibilities of playing with this powerful and robust tool.
             <a href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/features/">
              Please check all theme generator features.
             </a>
            </p>
            <p>
             <img alt="" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-4088" src="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/new_features21.jpg" style="border: 5px solid white; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.496094) 0px 0px 4px; margin: 30px auto; width: 95%;" title="new_features2"/>
            </p>

   jQuery(document).ready(function(e) {
	 jQuery('.close_tooltip_first-time').click(function(e){
		e.preventDefault();
		e.stopPropagation();
		jQuery.cookie('wptool_first_time', 'false', { expires: 1000 });
		jQuery('.tooltip_first-time').remove();
	 });

  <script type="text/javascript">
   var countries = {
	'CA': { //Canada
		'AB' : 'Alberta', 'BC' : 'British Columbia', 'MA' : 'Manitoba', 'NB' : 'New Brunswick', 'NL' : 'Newfoundland and Labrador', 'NT' : 'Northwest Territories', 'NS' : 'Nova Scotia', 'NU' : 'Nunavut', 'ON' : 'Ontario', 'PE' : 'Prince Edward Island', 'QU' : 'Qubec', 'SA' : 'Saskatchewan', 'YU' : 'Yukon'
	},
	'US' : { //USA
		'AL' : 'Alabama', 'AK' : 'Alaska', 'AZ' : 'Arizona', 'AR' : 'Arkansas', 'CA' : 'California', 'CO' : 'Colorado', 'CT' : 'Connecticut', 'DE' : 'Delaware', 
		'DC' : 'District of Columbia', 'FL' : 'Florida', 'GA' : 'Georgia', 'HI' : 'Hawaii', 'ID' : 'Idaho', 'IL' : 'Illinois', 'IN' : 'Indiana',
		'IA' : 'Iowa', 'KS' : 'Kansas', 'KY' : 'Kentucky', 'LA' : 'Louisiana', 'ME' : 'Maine', 'MD' : 'Maryland', 'MA' : 'Massachusetts', 'MI' : 'Michigan',
		'MN' : 'Minnesota', 'MS' : 'Mississippi', 'MO' : 'Missouri', 'MT' : 'Montana', 'NE' : 'Nebraska', 'NV' : 'Nevada', 'NH' : 'New Hampshire',
		'NJ' : 'New Jersey', 'NM' : 'New Mexico', 'NY' : 'New York', 'NC' : 'North Carolina', 'ND' : 'North Dakota', 'OH' : 'Ohio', 'OK' : 'Oklahoma',
		'OR' : 'Oregon', 'PA' : 'Pennsylvania', 'RI' : 'Rhode Island', 'SC' : 'South Carolina', 'SD' : 'South Dakota', 'TN' : 'Tennessee', 'TX' : 'Texas',
		'UT' : 'Utah', 'VT' : 'Vermont', 'VA' : 'Virginia', 'WA' : 'Washington', 'WV' : 'West Virginia', 'WI' : 'Wisconsin', 'WY' : 'Wyoming'
	}
	};

jQuery(document).ready(function() {
	if (jQuery('#country_id')) {
		jQuery('#country_id').change(function () {
			var country_id = jQuery('#country_id').val();

			var region_select = jQuery('#region_id'); //state
			if (region_select) {
				var first_option = jQuery('#region_id option:first');
				region_select.empty();
				region_select.append(first_option);
			}
			var states = countries[country_id];
			if (states) {
				if (region_select) {
					jQuery.each(states, function(key, title) {
						region_select.append(jQuery('&lt;option&gt;&lt;/option&gt;').attr('value', key).text(title));
					});
					region_select.show();
				}
				jQuery('#region').hide();//textbox
				region_select.val(jQuery('#region_selected_id').val());
			} else {
				jQuery('#region').show();//textbox
				region_select.hide();
			}
		});
		jQuery('#country_id').change();
		
		jQuery('#region_id').change(function() {
			jQuery('#region').val(jQuery("#region_id option:selected").text());
		});
	}
	
	if (jQuery('#billing_country_id')) {
		jQuery('#billing_country_id').change(function () {
			var country_id = jQuery('#billing_country_id').val();

			var region_select = jQuery('#billing_region_id'); //state
			if (region_select) {
				var first_option = jQuery('#billing_region_id option:first');
				region_select.empty();
				region_select.append(first_option);
			}
			var states = countries[country_id];
			if (states) {
				if (region_select) {
					jQuery.each(states, function(key, title) {
						region_select.append(jQuery('&lt;option&gt;&lt;/option&gt;').attr('value', key).text(title));
					});
					region_select.show();
				}
				jQuery('#billing_region').hide();//textbox
				region_select.val(jQuery('#billing_region_selected_id').val());
			} else {
				jQuery('#billing_region').show();//textbox
				region_select.hide();
			}
		});
		jQuery('#billing_country_id').change();

		jQuery('#billing_region_id').change(function() {
			jQuery('#billing_region').val(jQuery("#billing_region_id option:selected").text());
		});
	}

	if (jQuery('#shipping_country_id')) {
		jQuery('#shipping_country_id').change(function () {
			var country_id = jQuery('#shipping_country_id').val();

			var region_select = jQuery('#shipping_region_id'); //state
			if (region_select) {
				var first_option = jQuery('#shipping_region_id option:first');
				region_select.empty();
				region_select.append(first_option);
			}
			var states = countries[country_id];
			if (states) {
				if (region_select) {
					jQuery.each(states, function(key, title) {
						region_select.append(jQuery('&lt;option&gt;&lt;/option&gt;').attr('value', key).text(title));
					});
					region_select.show();
				}
				jQuery('#shipping_region').hide();//textbox
				region_select.val(jQuery('#shipping_region_selected_id').val());
			} else {
				jQuery('#shipping_region').show();//textbox
				region_select.hide();
			}
		});
		jQuery('#shipping_country_id').change();

		jQuery('#shipping_region_id').change(function() {
			jQuery('#shipping_region').val(jQuery("#shipping_region_id option:selected").text());
		});
	}
});
  </script>

   layout_number=1;
jQuery('#color_picker_demo').keyup(function(e) {
	jQuery('ul.menu_prueba li').css('color','#'+jQuery(this).val());
});

jQuery('#color_picker_demo').ColorPicker({
			color: '#666666',
			onShow: function (colpkr) {
				jQuery(colpkr).fadeIn(500);
				return false;
			},
			onHide: function (colpkr) {
				jQuery(colpkr).fadeOut(500);
				return false;
			},
			onChange: function (hsb, hex, rgb) {
				jQuery('#color_picker_demo').val(hex);
				jQuery('ul.menu_prueba li').css('color','#'+hex);
			}
});
function close_notify(){
	jQuery('div.notify').hide();
}
/*delete area */
function tg_delete(element){
	var r=confirm("are you sure you want to delete "+jQuery(element).attr('data-name')+'?');
	if (r==true){
		data='tg_delete='+jQuery(element).attr('data-id');
		jQuery('img.logout').show();
		jQuery.post(document.URL,data,
		function(data) {
			jQuery('img.logout').hide();
			jQuery(element).parent('li').remove();
		});
	}
}
/*logout area*/
function logout(){
	jQuery.removeCookie('session[id_user]');
	jQuery.removeCookie('session[login_in]');
	data='logout=1';
	jQuery('img.logout').show();
	jQuery.post(document.URL,data,
	function(data) {
		document.location.href="http://www.wpthemegenerator.com?wtgs=26104";
//		location.reload(true);
	});
}

		jQuery.post( ajaxurl,{ action:'tg_change_pathname', path_id:'90dde6a8b0',pathname:path_name,newpath:newpath,element_type:'menu'},function(data) {
			jQuery('div.set_header_menu ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');
			jQuery('div.set_header_menu ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).menu(this);" data-header-menu-height="'+data.img_height+'" data-header-menu-width="'+data.img_width+'" data-font_color="#'+color+'" data-font_size="'+get_ft_size+'" data-line_height="'+lh+'" data-current_margin="0" data-current_top="0" data-font_family="\'Trebuchet MS, Arial\', Helvetica, sans" data-current_height="" data-hover_menu="none"&gt;&lt;img src="'+data.path+'"  /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
			jQuery('div.set_header_menu ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
			jQuery('a[rel="option_header"]').trigger('click');
			jQuery('a[rel="set_header_menu"]').trigger('click');
			jQuery('div.set_header_menu').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_menu ul.get_thumb_list').height());
			jQuery('div.set_header_menu ul.get_thumb_list li:last a ').trigger('click');
			jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();
		},'json');
	}
}
function wtg_save_shadow(){
	get_value_opt=jQuery('input[name="tg_sh_opt"]:checked').val();
	switch (get_value_opt){
		case 'repeat-x':
			newpath=basename+'-repeat.png';
		break;
		case 'no-repeat':
			newpath=basename+'.png';
		break;
	}	
	jQuery.post( ajaxurl ,{ action:'tg_change_pathname', path_id:'90dde6a8b0',pathname:path_name,newpath:newpath,element_type:'shadows'},function(data) {
			jQuery('div.set_shadows ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).shadows(this);" data-shadow-block-height="'+data.img_height+'" data-menu-bar-width="'+data.img_width+'" data-repeat="'+get_value_opt+'"&gt;&lt;img src="'+data.path+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;').css('border','none');
			jQuery('div.set_shadows ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');						
			jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
			jQuery('a[rel="set_shadows"]').trigger('click');
			jQuery('div.set_shadows').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_shadows ul.get_thumb_list').height());	
			jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').hide();
	},'json');
 }
function change_ft_size(value,type){
	get_value=value+'px';
	switch(type){
		case 'font':
			jQuery('ul.menu_prueba li').css('font-size',get_value);
		break;
		case 'lh':
			jQuery('ul.menu_prueba li').css('line-height',get_value);		
		break;
	}
}
function click_file(id){
	jQuery('input[name="'+id+'"]').trigger('click');
}    
	jQuery(document).ready(function(e) {
		
  			var btnUpload=jQuery('#pattern');
		var status=jQuery('#status');
		new AjaxUpload(btnUpload, {
			action: ajaxurl,
			name: 'pattern',
			data: { action:'tg_upload_ele_user', upload_id :'7935cb5048',name:'pattern'},
			responseType:'json',
			onSubmit: function(file, ext){
				 if (! (ext &amp;&amp; /^(png|jpg)$/.test(ext))){ 
                    // extension is not allowed 
					status.text('Only PNG or JPG is allowed');
					return false;
				}
				status.text('Uploading...');
			},
			onComplete: function(file, response){

				switch (response.element){
					case 'pattern':
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');												
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).pattern(this);"  &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');							
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_gral_patterns"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'divisors':
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a  href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).divisors(this);" rel="" data-header-divisors-height="'+response.img_height+'" data-header-divisors-width="'+response.img_width+'" title="'+response.title+'"&gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_general_divisors"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'clipart':
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).clipart(this);" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_header_bkgimage"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'logo':
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');								
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\" rel=\"\" onclick=\"return jQuery(this).tg_logo();\" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_logo"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_logo').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last a ').trigger('click');
					break;
					case 'shadows':
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();					
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').show();						
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;						
						/*									*/
					break;
					case 'menu':
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').hide();						
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css('background-image','url('+response.path+')');
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css({'max-height':response.img_height+'px','height':response.img_height+'px'});
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').show();
						menu=true;
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;
					break;
					default:
						status.text( response.info ).show();
						return;
					break;					

				}
				//On completion clear the status
				status.html('');
				if (response.menu===false){
					menu=false;
					jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();
				}
				//Add uploaded file to list
			}
		});
				var btnUpload=jQuery('#logo');
		var status=jQuery('#status');
		new AjaxUpload(btnUpload, {
			action: ajaxurl,
			name: 'logo',
			data: { action:'tg_upload_ele_user', upload_id :'7935cb5048',name:'logo'},
			responseType:'json',
			onSubmit: function(file, ext){
				 if (! (ext &amp;&amp; /^(png|jpg)$/.test(ext))){ 
                    // extension is not allowed 
					status.text('Only PNG or JPG is allowed');
					return false;
				}
				status.text('Uploading...');
			},
			onComplete: function(file, response){

				switch (response.element){
					case 'pattern':

						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).pattern(this);"  &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');

						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'divisors':
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a  href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).divisors(this);" rel="" data-header-divisors-height="'+response.img_height+'" data-header-divisors-width="'+response.img_width+'" title="'+response.title+'"&gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_general_divisors"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'clipart':
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');

						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'logo':
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');								
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\" rel=\"\" onclick=\"return jQuery(this).tg_logo();\" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_logo"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_logo').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last a ').trigger('click');
					break;
					case 'shadows':
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();					
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').show();						
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;						
						/*									*/
					break;
					case 'menu':
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').hide();						
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css('background-image','url('+response.path+')');
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css({'max-height':response.img_height+'px','height':response.img_height+'px'});
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').show();
						menu=true;
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;
					break;
					default:
						status.text( response.info ).show();
						return;
					break;					

				}
				//On completion clear the status
				status.html('');
				if (response.menu===false){
					menu=false;
					jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();
				}
				//Add uploaded file to list
			}
		});

					case 'divisors':
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a  href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).divisors(this);" rel="" data-header-divisors-height="'+response.img_height+'" data-header-divisors-width="'+response.img_width+'" title="'+response.title+'"&gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_general_divisors"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'clipart':
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).clipart(this);" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_header_bkgimage"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'logo':
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');								
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\" rel=\"\" onclick=\"return jQuery(this).tg_logo();\" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_logo"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_logo').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last a ').trigger('click');
					break;
					case 'shadows':
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();					
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').show();						
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;						
						/*									*/
					break;
					case 'menu':
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').hide();						
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css('background-image','url('+response.path+')');
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css({'max-height':response.img_height+'px','height':response.img_height+'px'});
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').show();
						menu=true;
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;
					break;
					default:
						status.text( response.info ).show();
						return;
					break;					

				}
				//On completion clear the status
				status.html('');
				if (response.menu===false){
					menu=false;
					jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();
				}
				//Add uploaded file to list
			}
		});
				var btnUpload=jQuery('#menu');
		var status=jQuery('#status');
		new AjaxUpload(btnUpload, {
			action: ajaxurl,
			name: 'menu',
			data: { action:'tg_upload_ele_user', upload_id :'7935cb5048',name:'menu'},
			responseType:'json',
			onSubmit: function(file, ext){
				 if (! (ext &amp;&amp; /^(png|jpg)$/.test(ext))){ 
                    // extension is not allowed 
					status.text('Only PNG or JPG is allowed');
					return false;
				}
				status.text('Uploading...');
			},
			onComplete: function(file, response){

				switch (response.element){
					case 'pattern':
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');												
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li &gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).pattern(this);"  &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');							
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_gral_patterns"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_gral_patterns ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'divisors':
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a  href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).divisors(this);" rel="" data-header-divisors-height="'+response.img_height+'" data-header-divisors-width="'+response.img_width+'" title="'+response.title+'"&gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_general_divisors"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_general_divisors').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_general_divisors ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'clipart':
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');					
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#" rel="" onclick="return jQuery(this).clipart(this);" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_header_bkgimage"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
					break;
					case 'logo':
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','none');								
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').after('&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=\"#\" rel=\"\" onclick=\"return jQuery(this).tg_logo();\" &gt;&lt;img src="'+response.img_thumb+'" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;');
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last').css('border','3px solid yellow');
						jQuery('a[rel="option_global"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('a[rel="set_logo"]').trigger('click');
						jQuery('div.set_logo').scrollTop(jQuery('div.set_header_bkgimage ul.get_thumb_list').height());
						jQuery('div.set_logo ul.get_thumb_list li:last a ').trigger('click');
					break;
					case 'shadows':
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();					
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').show();						
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;						
						/*									*/
					break;
					case 'menu':
						jQuery('div.tg_shadow_opt').hide();						
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css('background-image','url('+response.path+')');
						jQuery('ul.menu_prueba').css({'max-height':response.img_height+'px','height':response.img_height+'px'});
						jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').show();
						menu=true;
						path_name=response.path_name;
						basename=response.basename;
					break;
					default:
						status.text( response.info ).show();
						return;
					break;					

				}
				//On completion clear the status
				status.html('');
				if (response.menu===false){
					menu=false;
					jQuery('div.menu_demo_ct').hide();
				}
				//Add uploaded file to list
			}
		});
						get_width_menu=jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.current-menu-ancestor').width();
		if (get_width_menu&gt;0){
			jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.back').css('width',get_width_menu+20);
		}else{
	  		get_width_menu=jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.current-menu-item').width();
			if (get_width_menu&gt;0){
				jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.back').css('width',get_width_menu+20);
			}
		}
//		console.log(jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.current-menu-ancestor').width());
//		jQuery('body .container_menu ul li.back').attr('style');
					if (sessvars.tg_themename){
				jQuery('div.cur_th_base button.tg_current').html('Current: '+sessvars.tg_themename);
			}

		/*load slider menu area */
		jQuery('div.menu-wtg-container ul.sub-menu a[title]').each(function(index, element) {
			jQuery(this).click(function(e) {
			  e.preventDefault()
		 	  var value=jQuery(this).attr('title');
              jQuery('input[value="'+value+'"]').trigger('click');
            });
        });

		
	});
  </script>
